{"tid":1868922,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[抵壘]  大批內地旅客申請延長逗留在港期限","createTime":"2020-02-08T00:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T03:25:27.000Z","uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"44203850a261fd9b28c011816c4cfa4562692d37","tid":1868922,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T00:24:18.000Z","msg":"大批內地旅客申請延長逗留在港期限<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=379721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D379721&d=%2FXNhycaKVB9NPWqbniWxn%2FkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=5dbd2d17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D379721&h=a84bca02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=379721</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】在入境事務大樓，大批內地旅客申請延長逗留在港期限。<br />\n<br />\n在入境事務大樓五樓延期逗留組的櫃台外，坐滿申請延期留港的人，當中不少是內地旅客。<br />\n<br />\n內地一般自由行來港簽證留港限期是七天，當局在2月1日起暫停發出自由行簽證，最後一批在這一兩天到期，如要延長留在時間，要向入境處申請獲得批准；持其他種類簽證的內地人如要延長留港，亦要獲得批准。<br />\n<br />\n有安徽旅客說當地疫情嚴峻、交通亦癱瘓，計劃申請留在香港多一段時間。"},{"pid":"e67fc9b7a094cea0e93d5fe26b25533d39de4981","tid":1868922,"uid":65449,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T00:28:19.000Z","msg":"仲俾佢地留喺度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7a1f4eec62b9d659d49d2a447efd221259190e","tid":1868922,"uid":276184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T00:30:00.000Z","msg":"原來仲可以咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb5d175b43a3690ad1e406dfb4630768a8d01b8","tid":1868922,"uid":313341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T00:34:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19be9f091a48e0bad077b645b90cfb088116730c","tid":1868922,"uid":99172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T01:11:40.000Z","msg":"有冇得唔批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"